---
import TerminalDemo from "./TerminalDemo.tsx";
---
<section class="relative px-6 pt-20 pb-16 md:pt-28 md:pb-24">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
		<!-- Two-column hero -->
		<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_1fr] gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start">

			<!-- LEFT: Headline + CTAs -->
			<div>
				<!-- Badge -->
				<a href="https://github.com/vinpatel/aeorank" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-accent-muted border border-accent/20 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm mb-8 hover:border-accent/40 transition-colors">
					<span class="text-accent font-semibold">Open source</span>
					<span class="text-text-muted">·</span>
					<span class="text-text-muted">40% of discovery is now AI</span>
					<span class="text-text-muted">·</span>
					<span class="text-text-muted">Free forever</span>
				</a>

				<h1 class="heading-xl">
					<span class="text-text">You rank #1 on Google.</span><br/>
					<span class="text-accent">AI can't see you.</span>
				</h1>

				<p class="text-text-secondary text-lg mt-6 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
					AI answers now drive 40% of web discovery — and they only cite sites they can read. AEOrank scores your AI visibility in 30 seconds, shows you exactly what's broken, then generates the 9 files that fix it. Free forever. Open source. No vendor lock-in.
				</p>

				<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-8">
					<a href="https://github.com/apps/aeorank" class="btn-primary !px-6 !py-3 text-base">Get Your Free AEO Score</a>
					<a href="#scoring" class="btn-secondary !px-6 !py-3 text-base">See How Scoring Works</a>
				</div>

				<p class="text-text-muted text-sm mt-5">
					Prefer terminal? <code class="!text-xs">npx aeorank-cli scan https://your-site.com</code><br/>
					Want CI gating? <a href="https://github.com/marketplace/actions/aeorank-aeo-scanner" class="text-accent hover:underline">Use the GitHub Action</a>.
				</p>

				<p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-4 italic">If ChatGPT is asked about your category, your name should appear. Right now, it probably doesn't.</p>
			</div>

			<!-- RIGHT: Quick start card -->
			<div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-bg-raised p-8 lg:mt-8">
				<div class="inline-block rounded-full bg-accent-muted border border-accent/20 px-4 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-accent uppercase tracking-wider mb-6">
					30 seconds to your first score
				</div>

				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Score. Fix. Ship.</h3>
				<p class="text-text-muted text-sm mb-6 leading-relaxed">Other tools charge $129/mo to tell you what's wrong. AEOrank tells you what's wrong, then fixes it — for free.</p>

				<!-- Numbered steps -->
				<div class="space-y-5">
					<div class="flex gap-4">
						<span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center text-accent text-sm font-bold">1</span>
						<div>
							<p class="font-semibold text-sm">Scan your site</p>
							<p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-0.5">GitHub App, CLI, or GitHub Action — pick one</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="flex gap-4">
						<span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center text-accent text-sm font-bold">2</span>
						<div>
							<p class="font-semibold text-sm">Get your AEO score (0–100)</p>
							<p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-0.5">36 criteria, 5 pillars, graded A+ through F</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="flex gap-4">
						<span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center text-accent text-sm font-bold">3</span>
						<div>
							<p class="font-semibold text-sm">Deploy the generated files</p>
							<p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-0.5">9 files — llms.txt, ai.txt, schema.json, and more</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<a href="https://github.com/apps/aeorank" class="btn-primary w-full justify-center mt-8">Install App →</a>

				<p class="text-text-muted text-xs text-center mt-3">Free forever · No credit card · MIT licensed</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Three feature cards -->
		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-16">
			<div class="card p-6">
				<span class="eyebrow text-green text-[11px]">Score</span>
				<h3 class="font-bold mt-2 mb-2">Know exactly where AI ignores you.</h3>
				<p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">36 deterministic checks across every major AI engine. No LLM calls, no black-box scores — same result every run, so you can track progress with confidence.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card p-6">
				<span class="eyebrow text-[11px]">Fix</span>
				<h3 class="font-bold mt-2 mb-2">Get the 9 files AI engines actually read.</h3>
				<p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">llms.txt, ai.txt, CLAUDE.md, schema.json, robots-patch, FAQ blocks, citation anchors, AI sitemap — all tailored to your site. No other tool generates these.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card p-6">
				<span class="eyebrow text-[#FFD700] text-[11px]">Ship</span>
				<h3 class="font-bold mt-2 mb-2">Never accidentally break your AI visibility.</h3>
				<p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">GitHub App posts AEO scores on every PR. GitHub Action blocks deploys that drop your score. One install. No YAML required.</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Demo terminal -->
		<div class="mt-16">
			<div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-[#0A0A0C] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-black/50">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 border-b border-border bg-white/[0.02]">
					<div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#FF5F57]"></div>
					<div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#FFBD2E]"></div>
					<div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#28C840]"></div>
					<span class="text-xs text-text-muted ml-2 font-mono">aeorank — terminal</span>
				</div>
				<TerminalDemo client:visible />
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Big stat cards -->
		<div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mt-16">
			<div class="card p-6 text-center animate-on-scroll">
				<div class="text-4xl font-bold text-accent">$0</div>
				<div class="text-text-muted text-sm mt-1">vs $129+/mo competitors</div>
			</div>
			<div class="card p-6 text-center animate-on-scroll">
				<div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#FFD700]">36</div>
				<div class="text-text-muted text-sm mt-1">Criteria. More than any competitor.</div>
			</div>
			<div class="card p-6 text-center animate-on-scroll">
				<div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#FFD700]">9</div>
				<div class="text-text-muted text-sm mt-1">AI files generated. None do this.</div>
			</div>
			<div class="card p-6 text-center animate-on-scroll">
				<div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#FFD700]">13</div>
				<div class="text-text-muted text-sm mt-1">Framework plugins. Zero config.</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Engines row -->
		<div class="text-center mt-12">
			<p class="eyebrow text-text-muted !text-[11px] !tracking-[0.15em] mb-4">OPTIMIZES VISIBILITY ACROSS EVERY MAJOR AI ENGINE</p>
			<div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 text-text-secondary text-sm">
				<span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-green text-lg">●</span> ChatGPT</span>
				<span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-green text-lg">●</span> Perplexity</span>
				<span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-green text-lg">●</span> Claude</span>
				<span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-green text-lg">●</span> Gemini</span>
				<span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-green text-lg">●</span> Google AI Overviews</span>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

